OL,3,CTributes paid to 'beloved mother' who
OL,4,Cdied in Leeds
OL,6,FA 51-year-old woman who died in Leeds
OL,7,Flast week has been named, while a
OL,8,Fmurder investigation remains ongoing.
OL,10,FGosia Wiktor was found seriously
OL,11,Finjured at an address on Foster
OL,12,FSquare, where she later died.
OL,14,FDetectives from the Homicide and Major
OL,15,FEnquiry Team launched a murder
OL,16,Finvestigation on Thursday 11 June.
