OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F331A1781542112
OL,3,CTributes paid to 'beloved mother' who
OL,4,Cdied in Leeds
OL,6,FIn a tribute her family said: "It is
OL,7,Fso hard to find words when our hearts
OL,8,Fare filled with sorrow. It will be so
OL,9,Fdifficult, and life will be so
OL,10,Fdifferent, learning to live without
OL,11,Fyou. We still cannot believe that we
OL,12,Fwill no longer hear your laughter, see
OL,13,Fyour smile...
OL,15,F"You left far too soon, leaving behind
OL,16,Fan emptiness that nothing can fill. As
OL,17,Fa beloved mother, daughter, sister,
OL,18,Faunt, cousin, you were the heart of
OL,19,Four family, a source of warmth, love,
OL,20,Fand joy.
OL,26,@nD@_OUwD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/3
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,332,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F331A1781542112
OL,3,CTributes paid to 'beloved mother' who
OL,4,Cdied in Leeds
OL,6,F"We are not able to say goodbye. The
OL,7,Fpain felt by our entire family is
OL,8,Fbeyond words. That is why we will not
OL,9,Fsay 'farewell,' because we believe
OL,10,Fthat love is stronger than death.
OL,11,FInstead, we will simply say: 'Stay
OL,12,Fclose.'
OL,14,F"Forever in our hearts and thoughts.
OL,15,FYour loving family."
OL,17,FA 52-year-old man who was arrested on
OL,18,Fsuspicion of Ms Wiktor's murder has
OL,19,Fnow been released from hospital and is
OL,20,Fin police custody.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUwD@TO]
